com.mobius.vdrapi
Class RenderFormatType

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.mobius.vdrapi.RenderFormatType
public final class RenderFormatType
extends Object

The RenderFormatType class enumerates the available document render formats, as suppported by the PageView class and the CreatePageGroupCommand command.

See Also:
CreatePageGroupCommand, Page, PageView
